{"tid":1604434,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"咁都唔撚明十月一要五區搞嘅同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-09-30T03:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T08:24:02.000Z","uid":63562,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ac87e93d75f9866857a21593f9034df490206fb3","tid":1604434,"uid":63562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"尋日發生乜事，有出去發夢嘅相信好清楚<br />\n啲狗晨咁早已經查車搜身，set roadblock<br />\n係SOGO都<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未撚起步</span></span>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">周圍已經tg放題</span></span></strong><br />\n話十一出晒去港島集人氣嘅！你同我講點集！？<br />\n我見到嘅只係一大班手足係到呆等<br />\n呆等&gt;tg放題&gt;狗衝出黎&gt;全部人跑&gt;跑得慢比人拉<br />\n到走果陣啦，個個又要換衫又要棄裝又要等家長車<br />\n<br />\n成日係到話要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">gimmick</span></span>，要有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">題材</span></span>比外國記者<br />\n十月一號<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他國</span></strong>國慶<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">我港多區起義賀佢老母</span></span></strong><br />\n隔一條河<br />\n一邊<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">深圳</span></strong>係到粉飾太平放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一邊<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港</span></strong>遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲唔夠觸目咩？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">HONG KONG IS NOT CHINA</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己區搞有乜好啊？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1.慳返撘車嘅時間<br />\n2.熟悉地形有利be water<br />\n3.可以隨時返屋企避<br />\n4.有街坊幫手(屌狗又好，派文具衫褲又好)<br />\n5.攞文具都方便啦(大西北人點帶個鋼錘出去?)<br />\n6.分散狗力狗車<br />\n7.減低被捕風險</strong><br />\n<br />\n咪撚再咁自私啦！經過尋日你仲同我吹風話出去！？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全部人同我推撚爆呢個po！！</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後祝各位武運昌隆"},{"pid":"6ff8f1d77b904a19b1cdf2676245387f94baf019","tid":1604434,"uid":75726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"贊成 近屋企可以快啲返屋企避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04647f96ebf9ad2a65d9168ad6c2d68e71272f1c","tid":1604434,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac87e93d75f9866857a21593f9034df490206fb3","tid":1604434,"uid":63562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"尋日發生乜事，有出去發夢嘅相信好清楚<br />\n啲狗晨咁早已經查車搜身，set roadblock<br />\n係SOGO都<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未撚起步</span></span>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">周圍已經tg放題</span></span></strong><br />\n話十一出晒去港島集人氣嘅！你同我講點集！？<br />\n我見到嘅只係一大班手足係到呆等<br />\n呆等&gt;tg放題&gt;狗衝出黎&gt;全部人跑&gt;跑得慢比人拉<br />\n到走果陣啦，個個又要換衫又要棄裝又要等家長車<br />\n<br />\n成日係到話要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">gimmick</span></span>，要有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">題材</span></span>比外國記者<br />\n十月一號<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他國</span></strong>國慶<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">我港多區起義賀佢老母</span></span></strong><br />\n隔一條河<br />\n一邊<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">深圳</span></strong>係到粉飾太平放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一邊<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港</span></strong>遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲唔夠觸目咩？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">HONG KONG IS NOT CHINA</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己區搞有乜好啊？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1.慳返撘車嘅時間<br />\n2.熟悉地形有利be water<br />\n3.可以隨時返屋企避<br />\n4.有街坊幫手(屌狗又好，派文具衫褲又好)<br />\n5.攞文具都方便啦(大西北人點帶個鋼錘出去?)<br />\n6.分散狗力狗車<br />\n7.減低被捕風險</strong><br />\n<br />\n咪撚再咁自私啦！經過尋日你仲同我吹風話出去！？<br /